# рџ›ЎпёЏ SentinelMind AI

> AI-powered Cybersecurity Incident Analysis & Memory Assistant built with FastAPI, HTML/CSS/JavaScript, SQLite, and Cognee.

---

## рџ“Њ Overview

SentinelMind AI is an intelligent cybersecurity incident management system that analyzes security incidents, classifies them using AI, stores them in a database, and remembers previous incidents using **Cognee Memory**.

Unlike traditional incident management tools that simply store records, SentinelMind AI allows analysts to retrieve similar historical incidents and reuse previous knowledge when responding to new threats.

